com.opengamma.strata.calc.runner.function.result

Class CurrencyValuesArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.calc.runner.function.result.CurrencyValuesArray
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CurrencyConvertible<CurrencyValuesArray>, ScenarioResult<CurrencyAmount>, Bean, ImmutableBean

    public final class CurrencyValuesArray
extends Object
implements CurrencyConvertible<CurrencyValuesArray>, ScenarioResult<CurrencyAmount>, ImmutableBean
    An array of currency values in one currency representing the result of the same calculation performed for multiple scenarios.

    This class is intended to be used as the return value from the execute method of implementations of CalculationSingleFunction and CalculationMultiFunction.

    Instances of this class will be automatically converted to the reporting currency by the calculation engine.
